{"tid":1856390,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"支那女人，寧死都要來香港","createTime":"2020-02-01T15:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T15:20:24.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84493dde2265a4316d81bce0035c19d039f12a37","tid":1856390,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:00:38.000Z","msg":"【封關變闖關？】雙程證婦人被拒入境  <br />\n於羅湖邊境洗手間割脈後，被送往北區醫院 <br />\n海關親屬：前線被抽調至未封關口岸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月29日下午，曾有婦人持雙程證於羅湖邊境進入香港被拒，其後進入洗手間割脈，已被送往北區醫院，暫未知道婦人有無發燒或其他病徵。<br />\n<br />\n親屬相當擔心前線海關的工作安全，直指局部封關無效，憂慮未來會有更多人利用此漏洞進入香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%8B%80%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-136188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259E%258B%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%258B%2580%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-136188&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=51a744e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%8B%80%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-136188</a>"},{"pid":"ac26d620af5cab3bca0cf3a8455172a9d0814888","tid":1856390,"uid":164813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:05:17.000Z","msg":"割下脈就入到有冇咁兒戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47e449b6c346d393f5cff3366b29cc62e534fd6","tid":1856390,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"「罷工」港龍員工需要支持！請幫忙宣傳！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83f9ffac4769a2a6446734c9972e20a294509f3a","tid":1856390,"uid":27946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T1